dcterms:description: A well-annotated EEG dataset collected from 134 subjects, containing both awake and overnight sleep data. The dataset will be publicly available.
dcterms:title: EEG Dataset

dcterms:description: For each subject, ∼1.8 hours of EEG recordings are image-evoked EEG signals, segmented into about 2000 samples paired with corresponding semantic labels.
dcterms:title: Image-Evoked Dataset

dcterms:description: For each subject, ∼1.8 hours of EEG recordings are audio-evoked EEG signals, segmented into about 2000 samples paired with corresponding semantic labels.
dcterms:title: Audio-Evoked Dataset

dcterms:description: For each subject, ∼7.2 hours of EEG recordings are TMR-related EEG signals, segmented into ∼1200 NREM 2/3 samples and ∼300 REM samples, each paired with corresponding semantic labels.
dcterms:title: TMR-Related Dataset
